test_even_range:
assert [2, 4, 6] == [4, 6]
  At index 0 diff: 2 != 4
  Left contains one more item: 6
  Full diff:
  - [4, 6]
  + [2, 4, 6]
  ?  +++
test_large_range:
assert [1, 2, 3] == [2, 3]
  At index 0 diff: 1 != 2
  Left contains one more item: 3
  Full diff:
  - [2, 3]
  + [1, 2, 3]
  ?  +++
